## React providers (`components2/providers/`)

### Category 1 ‚Äî Library providers (not replaceable by Zustand)

| Provider | Why keep |
| --- | --- |
| `AppShellSidebarProvider` | shadcn `useSidebar()` ‚Äî do not reimplement in Zustand |
| `AppShellTooltipProvider` | shadcn tooltip subtree + delay |
| `AppShellRootThemeProvider` | `next-themes` owns `<html>` class (`app/layout.tsx`) |

### Category 2 ‚Äî Server‚Üíclient prop providers (Zustand is wrong)

| Provider | Why keep |
| --- | --- |
| `RouteEnvelopeProvider` | Layout-resolved `RouteEnvelope` for `error.tsx` ‚Äî do not mirror into Zustand |

Pass **serializable** values only. RSC resolves authority; client reads via `useRouteEnvelope()`.

### Category 3 ‚Äî Bridge (intentional dual read path)

| Bridge | Pattern |
| --- | --- |
| `AppShellThemeBridge` | `useTheme()` ‚Üí `useAppShellStore.applyNextTheme` |

**DRY:** `next-themes` remains **source of truth**; Zustand is a **convenience mirror** for shell code that should not call `useTheme()` everywhere.

---

## Decision matrix

| Need | Use | Location |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Session, org, permissions, ERP data | RSC + `#lib/auth` / `#features/*` | Never Zustand |
| Initial page data | Server Component | Never TanStack Query as sole source |
| Cross-shell client UI (command open, density) | Zustand module store | `components2/stores/*.store.ts` |
| Client async (search, polling) | TanStack Query | Feature `client.ts` or route-colocated client |
| Form submit pending / validation errors | `useActionState` | Route-colocated actions |
| shadcn / next-themes / QueryClient | React provider | `components2/providers/` |
| Layout ‚Üí client error context | React provider + serializable value | e.g. `RouteEnvelopeProvider` |
| Compound widget internals | `createContext` inside `components2/ui/*` | Do not promote to app store |
| Afenda-wide UI via hand-rolled `createContext` | **Forbidden** | Use Zustand store instead |

---

## Anti-patterns (block merge)

- New `createContext` in `app/` or `lib/` for app-wide UI flags
- RSC or `server-only` module importing `components2/stores/*`
- Zustand holding `organizationId`, `permissions`, session, or ERP rows
- Replacing `SidebarProvider` with custom Zustand sidebar state
- Copying `RouteEnvelope` (or any layout authority) into Zustand
- Root layout wrapping the whole app in providers beyond `AppShellRootThemeProvider` + shell `AppShellProviders`
- Mixing Zustand `create()` and provider wrappers in the **same file** (`stores/` vs `providers/`)

---

## File split (never mix)

| Folder | Tool | Example |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `components2/stores/` | Zustand | `app-shell.store.ts` |
| `components2/providers/` | React context / library wraps | `sidebar-provider.client.tsx` |

See `shell-directory.mdc` for compose order in `app-shell-providers.client.tsx`.

