## State type quick reference

Full table also in `frontend-quality-contract.mdc` ¬ß7. **Providers are not deprecated** when a row says Zustand‚Äîuse both layers per categories above.

| Data type | Solution |
| --- | --- |
| Server reads (default) | Server Component |
| Client interactive async | TanStack Query |
| Simple global **client** UI state | Zustand (`components2/stores/`) |
| Library / server props / rare scoped Zustand | React provider (`components2/providers/`) |
| Component-local | `useState` / `useReducer` |
| Form / mutation UI | `useActionState` / Server Actions |
